data.description: Welcome home to this charming property with front desert landscaping and mature trees. Inside, Enjoy the living room with a large window for bountiful natural light. The eating-in kitchen features tile flooring, high ceilings, tile counters, and plenty of wood cabinetry. All bedrooms enjoy wood-look flooring & large closets. The spacious backyard with an RV gate is the ideal place for gatherings and relaxing. This home also comes equipped with a large storage shed in the backyard along with a bonus room that can be used for an office/shop/or game room. Don't let this opportunity go away!
